			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="2864">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>The reason I subscribe to <strong>The Sun</strong> is that you have the courage and good sense to leave a fine ass and a fine flower in the picture, where they belong [&ldquo;<a href="/article/1654">The Day I Got Buck-Naked with a Daisy on My Ass</a>,&rdquo; Lorenzo Wilson Milam, August 1995].</p>

<p>Keep up the good work.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Mike Schwager<br>Chicago, Illinois</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
